_sText:
Small to medium map, mostly underground. HDR lighting, hostages in two different locations, one hostage rescue area, 20 player map.

Setting is a ICBM underground missile site. Terrorists have taken hostages to get the return of their comrades from prison. 

Missile control rooms are in the lower area accessible from two directions, small rooms, small hallways low lighting make for a lot of fun.

I repaired the bsp ( fixed sounds, missing textures), sorry for the mixup.

PLEASE RE DOWNLOAD to fix your map.
